data.description:
*Price Improvement*
Welcome to the perfect family home nestled in a serene and peaceful neighborhood! This charming residence boasts four spacious bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and an array of modern updates that will leave you in awe. From the inviting covered patio to the secure fenced back yard, every detail has been carefully crafted to ensure comfort and tranquility. With a new roof completing the package, this home is ready to provide you with years of worry-free living.

As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the warm and inviting atmosphere that permeates throughout the house. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertainment. The living room features abundant natural light that fills the space, enhancing its inviting ambiance.

The kitchen is a chef's dream come true, with its modern appliances, ample counter space, and stylish cabinetry. Whether you're preparing a quick breakfast or hosting a dinner party, this culinary haven is sure to impress. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy dining area where cherished memories will be made as loved ones gather around for meals and conversations.

The four generously sized bedrooms provide comfortable retreats for everyone in the family. Each room offers plenty of space for personalization and relaxation. The primary bedroom is a true oasis, complete with an en-suite bathroom for added privacy and convenience.

One of the highlights of this remarkable home is the covered patio, where you can unwind and enjoy the fresh air in any weather. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue, this outdoor space is perfect for year-round enjoyment. The fenced back yard provides a safe and private haven for children and pets to play freely.

Additional features include a new roof, ensuring peace of mind and protection from the elements. The updates throughout the home, including modern fixtures, fresh paint, and upgraded flooring, contribute to the overall appeal and functionality of this stunning property.

Located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood, this home offers a sense of community that is often sought after but rarely found. The property includes a serene and fully stocked pond, inviting fishing enthusiasts and nature lovers to enjoy the tranquil waters. A centerpiece of the outdoor living space, the swimming pool beckons residents and guests to indulge in refreshing dips and leisurely swims. With its glistening waters, comfortable lounging areas, and surrounding landscaping, the pool area presents a stunning retreat. 

You'll appreciate the tranquility and security it provides while still being within easy reach of schools, shopping centers, parks, and major transportation routes.

Don't miss this opportunity to own a beautiful family home that offers comfort, convenience, and timeless charm. Schedule a showing today and start envisioning a lifetime of cherished memories in this exceptional residence!

Seller will provide a painting allowance with acceptable offer.
